<h4><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/8/24/21399749/apple-store-retail-singapore-floating-design-marina-bay-sands">首家「漂浮的苹果店」将落户新加坡</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1360912" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/store.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/store.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/store-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/store-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/store-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>The Verge 消息，苹果于新加坡的新直营店「Apple Marina Bay Sands」是全球首家「漂浮」的苹果店，这将成为新加坡第三家苹果直营店。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1360913" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EgMgAQMVoAAFT5g.jpeg" alt="" width="2048" height="1364" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EgMgAQMVoAAFT5g.jpeg 2048w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EgMgAQMVoAAFT5g-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EgMgAQMVoAAFT5g-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EgMgAQMVoAAFT5g-1024x682.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" /></p>
<p>在夜晚，Apple Marina Bay Sands 呈现出别样风格。苹果至今仍未公布门店的具体开业时间，但表示「快了」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1360914" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/re.gif" alt="" width="513" height="292" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/re.gif 513w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/re-360x205.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 513px) 100vw, 513px" /></p>
<p>作为预热，苹果还为该门店发布了预告短片<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/1f446.png" alt="👆" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />和壁纸<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/1f447.png" alt="👇" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1360915" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Apple_Marina_Bay_Sands_Wallpaper-Download_Macbook_2880x1800_2x.jpg" alt="" width="5760" height="3600" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Apple_Marina_Bay_Sands_Wallpaper-Download_Macbook_2880x1800_2x.jpg 5760w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Apple_Marina_Bay_Sands_Wallpaper-Download_Macbook_2880x1800_2x-360x225.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Apple_Marina_Bay_Sands_Wallpaper-Download_Macbook_2880x1800_2x-768x480.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Apple_Marina_Bay_Sands_Wallpaper-Download_Macbook_2880x1800_2x-1024x640.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5760px) 100vw, 5760px" /></p>
<h4><a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-08-25/nintendo-plans-upgraded-switch-console-and-major-games-for-2021">任天堂明年将推出新 Switch 和系列游戏</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1360916" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/drer.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/drer.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/drer-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/drer-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/drer-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>《彭博社》援引知情人士消息称，任天堂将于明年推出新款的 Switch 主机和一系列新游戏。任天堂今年基本不会有太多大动作，也会跳过今年的假期档，避免和索尼以及微软的更新撞期。</p>
<p>目前，新主机的配置还没最终确认，但任天堂已经在考虑更强算力和 4K 画质。至于新游戏，消息称将来自任天堂内部和其它公司，面向囊括了深度玩家和轻度玩家的广泛人群。</p>
<h4><a href="http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2020-08-26/1489842.html">七夕单日票房超 5 亿元，创复工后单日最高纪录</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1360919" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020_0825_071917c6j00qfllvu01o4c002p801stc-1.jpg" alt="" width="3466" height="1974" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020_0825_071917c6j00qfllvu01o4c002p801stc-1.jpg 3466w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020_0825_071917c6j00qfllvu01o4c002p801stc-1-360x205.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020_0825_071917c6j00qfllvu01o4c002p801stc-1-768x437.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020_0825_071917c6j00qfllvu01o4c002p801stc-1-1024x583.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3466px) 100vw, 3466px" /></p>
<p>猫眼专业版数据显示，七夕单日票房达 5.093 亿元，创下了全国影院复工以来单日票房最高的纪录。其中，《我在时间尽头等你》上映首日票房达 2.65 亿元，《八佰》当日票房超 1.86 亿元，累计票房已达 11.50 亿元。</p>
<p>今年七夕的票房稍低于去年的 5.69 亿票房。除了因为去年有《哪吒》和《使徒行者 2》等影片在映，今年七夕时影院也未完全复工，上座率也有限制。</p>
<h4>最新疫情数字</h4>
<p><strong>国内（不含港澳台）</strong>：8 月 25 日，新增确诊病例 15 例，均为境外输入病例（四川 5 例，上海 4 例，广东 4 例，天津 1 例，云南 1 例）；无新增死亡病例；无新增疑似病例。</p>
<p><strong>香港</strong>：8 月 24 日，新增 19 例确诊病例，其中 3 例输入性病例，16 例本地确诊病例。香港食物及卫生局宣布，除非疫情出现突发逆转，将放宽社交距离措施。</p>
<p><strong>海外</strong>：截至 8 月 26 日 7 时，海外累计确诊病例 23871824 例，累计死亡 815948 例，累计治愈 16620048 例。</p>
